#Title : Multiple Reflected XSS in Webmin 2.402

# Researcher: Aarya Dahal
# vendor : https://webmin.com/
# Version Affected : 2.402
# Date 11 september 2025

Proof of Concept

1. Set up and installed Webmin 2.402 in a Linux testing environment.
2. Reviewed and tested various URLs.
3. Identified three specific URLs vulnerable to Reflected Cross-Site Scripting (XSS).
 https://localhost:10000/apache/?xnavigation=1
 https://localhost:10000/samba/edit_fshare.cgi?xnavigation=1
 https://localhost:10000/samba/save_pshare.cgi?xnavigation=1
4. Inserted payloads on the parameters 
 Document Root
 Share Name
 Share Name
5. The payload used JavaScript: <script>alert(1)</script>
6. The xss will execute on all the parameters
